{"tid":1047941,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"彈舌音","createTime":"2019-03-05T09:49:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-07T12:28:22.000Z","uid":99086,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ee9e9b5c939dc9b7306ca4f6e31fb8e87c5e41bf","tid":1047941,"uid":99086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T09:49:20.000Z","msg":"有無巴絲可以講解下西班牙文或俄文之類語言既彈舌音要點樣練習<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n<br />\n我自己練到好似啲阿伯咳痰咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實係咪我有啲位做錯左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n正確應該係要點？<br />\n<br />\n另外識吹口哨會唔會易啲學識彈舌音？<br />\n我個concept係 因為大家都要用到氣去幫助發音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁諗係咪好on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講到尾 我都係想請教下點樣發出彈舌音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：睇過9成youtube既教學片<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebd2110c31161e8065adb09a2ca3da1cc0f396ad","tid":1047941,"uid":99086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T09:49:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5687663216c2f5481bc31557e3a1bc40d5433860","tid":1047941,"uid":99086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T09:53:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22e6e7647e0d9c931c6441eb972b61bcaa42570a","tid":1047941,"uid":99086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T09:58:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ea911845bb832977d4094c2dc114a9d0ae7070f","tid":1047941,"uid":99086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T10:01:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1ed8e45ae71c28e42f1